author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the future where we now have Robots piloted by people on the other side of the world watching everything we do. Robots we also have to pay for the privilege of looking into our lives to "learn" from. Thanks for watching!

title: This Is Really Bad...
